snippet.title: Yuoni [PS4/PS5/XOne/XSX/PC] Trailer
snippet.description:
Yuoni is a gorgeous, sunset-stained first-person narrative horror game.


More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15603-yuoni/


Yuoni is coming to PC (Steam), PS4 and PS5 on August 19, 2021 with an Xbox release following very shortly after.
